CustomField.description: This field shows either the Total Archived formula field used on Single Institution records OR the Total Archived roll up summary used on Multi Institution records
CustomField.formula:
IF( Total_Archived_RollUp__c != 0 || Total_Archived_RollUp__c != null, Total_Archived_RollUp__c,
Total_Archived__c)
CustomField.label: Total # Archived
